    "title": "#國外遊記 國際語言志工招募！寒假邊玩邊當志工的好選擇～\n國立清華大學\n11 月 28 日 14:14\n寮國那坤國小語言教學志工招募 🇱🇦 寮國萬榮的【那坤國小】\n因為經費不足，目前只有約 40 位學生、2 位老師，學校需要外來的教學支援，才能繼續辦學。 \n\n我們想找的是：願意到現場陪孩子、教任何語言的人 不管你會中文、英文、泰文、越文，甚至母語都行，只要你肯教，就是幫忙。 \n\n📍地點：寮國萬榮 Nakhoun National Primary School \n\n👧👦學生：約 40 位 \n\n📚內容：語言教學（不限語言） \n\n🗓時間：可自訂，幾天、幾週都可以 \n\n💌聯絡：jupeter882000@gmail.com（張君松老師） \n\n👉 這不只是志工，也是一次很划算就能深入當地、體驗寮國在地文化和生活的機會。 \n👏也可以到隔壁的泰國一起玩個幾天，收穫滿滿。\n⸻ Language Teaching Volunteers Needed in Laos 🇱🇦 Nakhoun National Primary School in Vang Vieng, Laos currently has about 40 students and only 2 teachers. To keep the school running, they need volunteer teachers to help with language classes. We’re looking for people who: can teach any language and are willing to spend time with the kids. Chinese, English, Thai, your mother tongue — all welcome. \n\n📍Location: Nakhoun National Primary School, Vang Vieng, Laos \n👧👦Students: around 40 \n📚Teaching: any language \n🗓Duration: flexible (a few days, weeks, or longer) \n💌Contact: jupeter882000@gmail.com (Mr. Chang Chun-Sung) \n\n👉 It’s not only meaningful volunteering — it’s also a budget-friendly way to explore local Lao culture and daily life.",
